ne,\\\" Bach said.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999677659167, \"rank\": 3.2234137001718216e-08, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long journey\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a wonderful Olympic Village, and all the ingredients for a great Olympic Games are here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wonderful Olympic Village\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"all the ingredients\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"a great Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The venues are not only breathtaking; they are of the highest standard.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The venues\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest standard\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You feel how the enthusiasm in France is growing, and I hope you have the same feeling,\\\" the IOC boss added.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999521171444055, \"rank\": 3.325676233268003e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2210143324510987e-23, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"